dc_description_s: Scale 1:1,013,760 ; Statute miles, 16 = 1 in. (W 97⁰15ʹ--W 89⁰30ʹ/N 49⁰23ʹ--N 43⁰30ʹ). Red overprinting shows railroads. Title from upper margin. Title near copyright: Rand, McNally & Co.'s business atlas map of Minnesota. On verso: Minnesota. Counties, creeks, Indian reservations, lakes, rivers, and towns. Index in left margin. Includes list of "Minnesota Railroads." Insets: N.E. corner of state of Minnesota -- Minneapolis, St. Paul and vicinity. 66 x 48 cm
